data.description: Welcome Home!  You will fall in love as soon as you enter this light and bright, meticulously maintained, CBS, 3 bed, 3 bath PLUS office, pool home. Double entry doors lead you to spacious living room featuring a stacked stone, wood-burning fireplace; perfect for those cool evenings. Beautiful kitchen with warm wood cabinets, granite counters, and s/s appliances is the heart of the home. Kitchen opens to family room and affords clear views of your expansive paver patio, salt water pool with waterfall, and tropical, fenced backyard. Split floorplan. Third bed/bath suite with separate entrance and additional living/dining space!  Master suite has bonus space that can be a nursery, office, or fitness area.  Spa-like master bath with dual vanities, oversized soaking tub and separate walk-in shower with custom tile and multiple shower heads.  This home is built for entertaining or enjoying a quiet evening with family.  Newer standing seam metal roof (2021).  No HOA so bring your toys!
